 -3 \, x_{1} &  -  & 2 \, x_{2} &  +  & 11 \, x_{3} & = & -9 \\
 -x_{1} &  +  & 3 \, x_{2} &  &  & = & 8 \\
 &  -  & x_{2} &  +  & x_{3} & = & -3 \\
 \end{matrix}\] 

